name: avenue dress
description: A comfortable utilitarian dress can be worn in the spring and summer on it’s own, and with layers in the fall in winter. Available in cotton prints or solids. Customize this dress by sending your measurements and requesting different sleeve, skirt, or pocket styles, a different waistline or neckline, or a collar. Also available with a belt, sash or ribbon.

options.name: gray with pink dots and striped sash, size L
custom avenue dress, send info to ruthiesuniform@gmail.com

name: boulevard jacket
description: Worn over a dress or with an ensemble, this cute jacket adds the perfect amount of warmth and coverage for spring and summer, and can be worn with layers in fall and winter. Available in heavy cotton or blended fabric solids and designs. Customize this jacket by sending your measurements and requesting different sleeve lengths or collar styles and add buttons or pockets. You may also request a long version of this jacket with a sash or belt.

options.name: blue gray boulevard jacket, size S
custom boulevard jacket, send info to ruthiesuniform@gmail.com

name: street skirt
description: This simple classic skirt can be worn any time of the year. Available in cotton or blended fabric, solids and prints. Customize this skirt by sending your measurements and requesting a different or hem length or style, different pockets or no pockets, and details such as adding ribbon or trim.

options.name: blue gray street skirt, size M/L
custom street skirt, send info to ruthiesuniform@gmail.com

name: thruway blouse
description: This extremely comfortable blouse can be worn as a layer or on it’s own at any time of the year. Available in soft jersey fabrics, prints and solids, dependant on what can be found. Customize this blouse by sending your measurements and requesting a different neckline, sleeve length or style, add pockets or another color in the cuffs or details.

options.name: custom thruway blouse, send info to ruthiesuniform@gmail.com

name: canal hat
description: Hats! Available in heavy cotton, wool and blended fabrics, prints and solids. Customize this hat by sending your measurements and requesting different colors, details such as bow, flower or button, or keep it simple and leave the details out. The bill size and style can also be adjusted. Men’s hats available too, send a description and I’ll see what I can do!!

custom hat, send info to ruthiesuniform@gmail.com
